        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1786265769" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11518336999535916531">“The moving hand once having writ moves on. Nor all thy piety nor wit can lure it back to cancel half a line.” Some of the most beautiful poetry I have ever read...I read this book when I feel down and always find a line or two that lifts me up.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


